data.description:
Updated and spacious 3 bed 2 bath home located in the quiet and established Western Hills neighborhood of Fort Worth! Interior features include great natural lighting with replaced windows throughout, vaulted ceilings in large living area, kitchen with tons of cabinetry and storage, quartz countertops, and stainless steel appliances, fridge that stays. Large front formal doubles as a second living area, office, and-or dining room. Fresh paint and new flooring in bedrooms. Exterior boasts mature trees, beautiful landscaping and a fully fenced in backyard with large covered patio deck. New water heater installed in 2022. Irrigation system installed in 2021. Convenient access to shopping, dining, and entertainment. Landlord requirements include a min 640 credit score, income 3x monthly rent, clean background and rental history with no previous evictions, convictions, or broken leases. Small pets okay on a case-by-case basis.

One year minimum lease term. 
No smoking.
Small pets okay on a case-by-case basis.
